                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        204,
                                        2448,
                                        1252,
                                        2847
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": " is considered a hyperparameter of the problem; table "
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        204,
                                        2448,
                                        1252,
                                        2847
                                    ],
                                    "type": "inline_equation",
                                    "content": "\\mathbb{I}"
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        204,
                                        2448,
                                        1252,
                                        2847
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": " has a complete list of all hyperparameters used for MARLIN. For the choice of "
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        204,
                                        2448,
                                        1252,
                                        2847
                                    ],
                                    "type": "inline_equation",
                                    "content": "N"
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        204,
                                        2448,
                                        1252,
                                        2847
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": " , we followed the empirical considerations made in [24], and chose 10 as the length of the history after some preliminary trials and evaluations. During the training process, observations are processed and normalized through a moving average by using the VecNormalize environment wrapper present in SB3."
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    ],
                    "index": 6
                },
                {
